Jason   Shiver  Executive Advisor, Amplify Snack Brands, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 0 Board Members in 0 different organizations across 1 different industries.44$990,710As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. Jason Shiver has been North America President and Executive Vice President at Amplify Snack Brands, Inc. since October 6, 2016. prior to that, Mr. Shiver served as the Executive Vice President of Sales & Marketing at Amplify Snack Brands, Inc. from December 2014 to October 6, 2016 and as its Senior Vice President of Sales from July 2014 December 2015. Mr. Shiver served as Vice President of Sales at SkinnyPop from May 2013 to July 2014. From April 2012 to December ... 2013, he served as General Manager and Senior Vice President of Sales for Rickland Orchards, LLC, a yogurt snack company. From February 2008 to March 2012, Mr. Shiver served as the Senior Vice President of Sales and Marketing at Glutino USA, Inc., a gluten-free snack food company, which was acquired by Boulder Brands, Inc., a diversified food company. From May 2003 to January 2008, Mr. Shiver held several roles at Atkins Nutritionals, Inc., the leader in low-carb foods and beverages, including Vice President of Sales. From September 2001 to May 2003, he was a Southeast Regional Sales Manager at Acirca, Inc., an organic foods and beverages company. From August 2000 to September 2001, he was a National Account Manager at Arizona Beverages USA LLC. Mr. Shiver holds a Bachelor of Science in Marketing from University of South Florida.Read Full Background




